Tweets by Elite_Wealth 





Attention Investors:







Prevent Unauthorised Transactions in your Trading / Demat account –> Update your Mobile Number with your Depository Participant. Receive alerts on your Registered Mobile for all debit and other important transactions in your demat account directly from NSDL on the same day …..Issued in the interest of investors. KYC is one time exercise while dealing in securities markets – once KYC is done through a SEBI registered intermediary (Broker, DP, Mutual Fund etc.), you need not undergo the same process again when you approach another intermediary.”Prevent Unauthorized transactions in your account –> Update your mobile numbers/email IDs with your stock brokers. Receive information of your transactions directly from Exchange on your mobile/email at the end of the day ………. Issued in the interest of investors”







Contact Us 9:30 am To 6:00 pm Call : 011-42445800,   Mail : contact@elitewealth.in
















